Subject: [PATCH] mac80211: mesh: Free ie data when leaving mesh
Git-commit: 6a01afcf8468d3ca2bd8bbb27503f60dcf643b20
Patch-mainline: v5.8 or v5.8-rc8 (next release)
References: git-fixes

